criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Couples are required to have a stable relationship and live together in the last 3
             months;

          -  Older than 18 years and younger than 60 years; without regard to CD4 count;

          -  Open cohort(any newly diagnosed serodiscordant couples who are eligible for treatment
             will be included during the study period).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Couples are not have a stable relationship or do not live together in the last 3
             months;

          -  Younger than 18 years old.
